### **Summary of ASX Announcement – Midas Minerals Ltd (ASX: MM1)**  
**Announcement Type:** General Meeting Results  

- **All resolutions passed**, including:  
  - **Ratification of Tranche 1 Placement Shares** (Listing Rules 7.1 and 7.A) – **99.99% approval**.  
  - **Approval of Tranche 2 Placement Shares** – **99.99% approval**.  
  - **Approval of Director Placement Shares** (Sara Kelly, Mark Calderwood, Michael Wilson) – **99.99% approval each**.  
  - **Approval of Advisor Options** – **99.99% approval**.  

**No material capital or trading impact disclosed** (no new funding amounts, dates, or structural details provided).
